            </a>
          </p>

          <p><a href="mailto:hello@statemottoprints.com" class="footer-email">hello@statemottoprints.com</a></p>
          <p>Copyright Â© 2019 State Motto Prints. <br class="mobile-only"> All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <div hidden id="snipcart" data-api-key="OGViYzU1YTYtMjg2MC00M2UwLWE0ODEtMmQ4ZWI5ZDIyNDg2NjM3MjAxNTEwMjI3MzMzNDI0"></div>

    <script src="/javascripts/base.js" type="module"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.snipcart.com/themes/v3.0.10/default/snipcart.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
